This project contains modifications to the original GPUStack software,
including but not limited to:

- Custom model provider with dual-format (OpenAI/Anthropic) support
- Format conversion between Anthropic Messages API and OpenAI Chat Completions API
- Dual base URL and dual auth style configuration for custom providers
- Enhanced model list fetching with versioned API path handling
- Robust upstream response parsing for various provider formats
- Strip non-core fields option for non-standard providers
